 circulation around it. We discuss the relevance of this transition for\ntemporary captures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Apr 2019 16:00:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 13 Jan 2020 15:54:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-19"}
