ray luminosity confirming a similar dependence with index\n$-1.20\\pm0.36$ which we find as well in the GeV luminosity, both expressed in\nthe rest-frame. We thus discover in the realm of relativistic astrophysics the\nexistence of a self-similar physical process and power-law dependencies,\nextensively described in the micro-physical world by the classical works of\nHeisenberg-Landau-Wilson.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Apr 2019 16:14:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-09"}
