ained within 24 hours on a single GPU.\nOur model consistently outperforms state-of-the-art dynamic recommendation\nmethods, with up to 18% improvement in recall and 10% in mean reciprocal rank.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Apr 2019 22:15:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Apr 2019 17:15:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-14"}
