 with negative real\npart with probability tending to one. Our results shed a new light and\ncomplement the understanding of feasibility and stability issues for large\nbiological communities with interaction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Apr 2019 09:24:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-10"}
