wardly for predictions of properties of fluid mixtures using\nestablished combination rules. Input errors are a major source of errors in\nsimulations. The MolMod database contributes to reducing such errors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Apr 2019 09:18:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-11"}
