at commissioning and highlight the relevant steps and milestones\nachieved each time. Finally, we describe the successful cooldown of CUORE.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Apr 2019 00:16:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 12 Jul 2019 13:28:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-15"}
